  <oversight_info>
    <has_dmc>No</has_dmc>
  </oversight_info>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Total intra-venous anesthesia can be provided using a closed-loop system guided by the
      bispectral index. The purpose of this study is to determine if myorelaxation modifies its
      functioning.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
